@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

' Definicja aktora
actor "Player" as player

' Granice systemu
rectangle "Smart Pool Assistant System" {
    
    ' Przypadki użycia zdefiniowane w rozdziale 3
    usecase "UC-1: System Setup\n(Connect Android via ADB)" as UC1
    usecase "UC-2: Aiming Assistance\n(Ghost Ball AR Visualization)" as UC2
    usecase "UC-3: Stroke Execution\n& Biometric Analysis" as UC3
    usecase "UC-4: Review History\n(Performance Stats)" as UC4

}

' Relacje (Aktor -> Przypadek Użycia)
player --> UC1
player --> UC2
player --> UC3
player --> UC4

' Notatki wyjaśniające moduły (opcjonalne, ale ładnie wyglądają)
note bottom of UC1 : Requires Phone (Sensor Module)\n& PC (Vision Module)
note bottom of UC2 : Uses Computer Vision\n& Cue Detection
note bottom of UC3 : Triggered by Accelerometer\nPeak Detection (F=ma)

@enduml